info:
  Set Environment Variables And Values
  To See Environment Variables Used in Performing Actions Like building Bombs or Malwares execute 'show options'

Usage:

   Value Holder Name   Value To Hold
      __________         _________
lset     name              value
        -------           -------
           1                 2

example:

  lset LHOST 127.0.0.1
  lset LPORT 4444
  
  lset PLATFORM windows
  lset MALWARE  keylogger


